brand-docs
Copyright (c) 2026 Ferdinando Bonsegna

This M1 implementation is original MIT-licensed code. It does not vendor
proprietary Office helper scripts and does not include customer template assets.

This implementation uses python-docx, python-pptx, openpyxl, and lxml for
OOXML manipulation; Pillow for image processing. The OOXML resolver, profile
schema, QA gate, and CLI are custom-implemented from scratch.
